'''奧古斯都·奧登'''（Augusto Daniel Odone，{{bd|1933年|3月6日|2013年|10月25日|catIdx=Odone}}），[[世界銀行|世界銀行]][[經濟學家|經濟學家]]<ref name="AugustoObit">{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/culture-obituaries/10402968/Augusto-Odone.html |title=Augusto Odone - Telegraph |access-date=2013-10-26 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227133951/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/culture-obituaries/10402968/Augusto-Odone.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其兒子是[[罕見疾病|罕見疾病]][[腎上腺腦白質失養症|腎上腺腦白質失養症]]（ALD）的患者[[羅倫佐·奧登|羅倫佐·奧登]]。他們研發出飲用[[三油酸甘油酯|三油酸甘油酯]]（glycerol trioleate）與[[三芥子酸甘油脂|三芥子酸甘油脂]]（glycerol trierucate）的混合油的療法，這種油後來便稱為「[[羅倫佐的油|羅倫佐的油]]」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/2062622/Obituary-Lorenzo-Odone.html|title=Lorenzo Odone Subject of Lorenzo's Oil, the film portraying his parents' quest to cure his degenerative disease|date=1 Jun 2008|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=14 June 2010|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226220641/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/2062622/Obituary-Lorenzo-Odone.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有一部同名電影《[[羅倫佐的油_(電影)|羅倫佐的油]]》來描述羅倫佐的故事<ref>{{cite web | title=About Lorenzo, his Parents, and Oumouri | work=The Myelin Project | url=http://www.myelin.org/en/cms/?15 | accessdate=2010-01-02 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080903102051/http://www.myelin.org/en/cms/?15 | archivedate=2008-09-03 }}</ref>。

奧古斯都·奧登獲得[[斯特靈大學|斯特靈大學]][[名譽博士|名譽博士]]學位。他繼續籌集資金，推動科學專案直到他去世為止。

